WORKDIR /code

    build-base openssl-dev pkgconfig libffi-dev \
    cups-dev jpeg-dev && \

    pip install --no-cache-dir -r /code/requirements/requirements.txt && \
    apk del .build-deps

COPY . ./
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -e .
RUN aws-gate bootstrap

ENTRYPOINT ["aws-gate"]
CMD ["--help"]
